1
00:00:00,670 --> 00:00:01,870
Remember the "Personality".
牢記“人格”

2
00:00:03,310 --> 00:00:06,030
I met a girl today. Her name is Nevra Elmas.
我今天遇到一個女孩，她叫內夫拉·埃爾馬斯

3
00:00:08,470 --> 00:00:10,030
Do you have something to tell me Binnaz?
你有話要跟我說嗎？賓納茲

4
00:00:11,430 --> 00:00:15,030
She is the only one I trust. Because Nevra understands me.
她是我唯一信任的人，因為內夫拉了解我

5
00:00:34,950 --> 00:00:38,110
It's Nevra's birthday today. I got her a present.
今天是內夫拉的生日，我送她一份禮物

6
00:00:39,190 --> 00:00:42,790
Has your brother Tayyar ever mentioned a girl named Reyhan?
你的兄弟塔亞爾有冇有提到過一個叫雷漢的女孩嗎？

7
00:00:44,670 --> 00:00:47,190
He used to say "they wasted her", not "I wasted her".
他曾經說的是“他們糟蹋了她”，而不是“我糟蹋了她”

8
00:00:47,710 --> 00:00:52,310
I told you, I haven't done anything. I only threw a small piece of stone.
我告訴過你，我什麼都冇做  我隻扔了一小塊石頭

9
00:00:54,830 --> 00:00:56,910
Me and Nevra share a secret.
我和內芙拉分享了一個秘密

10
00:00:59,070 --> 00:01:02,030
Cemil almost owns whole of Kambura.
塞米爾幾乎擁有整個坎佈拉

11
00:01:03,110 --> 00:01:05,310
Nothing ever takes place without his knowledge.
如果冇有他的話什麼事都辦不成

12
00:01:05,950 --> 00:01:11,070
If it is as precious as to be hidden under a pillow...
如果它被藏在枕頭下  那麼珍貴的東西

13
00:01:11,190 --> 00:01:13,030
it was more likely a diary.
它更可能是一本日記

14
00:01:13,270 --> 00:01:16,310
I told Nevra everything. But she doesn't believe me.
我把一切都告訴了內芙拉，但她不相信我

15
00:01:35,630 --> 00:01:37,630
You are not speaking to your friend in Ankara.
你不是在跟安卡拉的朋友通話

16
00:01:37,830 --> 00:01:40,030
I don't think you should ever speak to him again anyway.
我不認為你應該再跟他通話了

17
00:01:40,110 --> 00:01:42,830
Save his a..ss and save your own.
救他一命  也救你自己一命

18
00:01:45,350 --> 00:01:47,750
We need someone to sort him out.
我們需要一個人來解決他

19
00:01:48,630 --> 00:01:52,550
I will burn that gypsy so bad they will ever dare to return to Kambura.
我將把吉普賽人燒死，以至於他們甚至都不敢再回到坎佈拉

20
00:01:54,510 --> 00:01:55,950
Tayyar remembers you.
塔亞爾記得你

21
00:02:01,190 --> 00:02:03,270
He said "they wasted the poor girl".
他說：“他們糟蹋了那個可憐的女孩”

22
00:02:03,710 --> 00:02:04,790
Hello Reyhan.
你好雷漢

23
00:02:07,190 --> 00:02:09,590
If Tayyar remembers, so do the others.
如果塔亞爾記得，其他人也記得

24
00:02:14,070 --> 00:02:16,510
All of them, they all remember.
他們所有人，他們都記得

25
00:02:21,510 --> 00:02:23,470
Whole of Kambura remembers.
整個坎佈拉都記得

26
00:02:24,990 --> 00:02:26,750
They just pretend that they don't.
他們隻是假裝自己不記得

27
00:05:18,710 --> 00:05:20,110
Don't pull the trigger.
別開槍

28
00:05:20,870 --> 00:05:22,070
Because I won't.
因為我不會開槍的

29
00:05:25,710 --> 00:05:29,310
The scene will be catastrophic, God forbid if one of these glasses break.
如果開槍的話現場將是災難性的，如果其中一塊玻璃碎了，上帝保佑。

30
00:05:36,390 --> 00:05:37,590
So intriguing.
真有趣

31
00:05:39,230 --> 00:05:41,070
Once I saved a fish's live.
曾經我救了一條魚

32
00:05:48,030 --> 00:05:50,110
Now they are saving my life.
現在他們救了我的命

33
00:05:51,750 --> 00:05:54,350
I don't think you've come here to kill me anyway.
我不認為你是來殺我的

34
00:05:56,110 --> 00:05:59,150
I tell you what's best...
我告訴你最好的方案……

35
00:05:59,270 --> 00:06:02,430
we both put the guns down...
我們倆都放下了槍

36
00:06:02,550 --> 00:06:04,270
and start from scratch.
從頭開始

37
00:06:04,710 --> 00:06:06,150
Right from the beginning.
重新開始

38
00:07:48,590 --> 00:07:49,990
Nevra, where are you?
內芙拉，你在哪裏？

39
00:07:50,310 --> 00:07:52,190
I am at the station in Kambura.
我在坎佈拉警局

40
00:07:52,390 --> 00:07:54,000
The girl we're looking for is definitely Reyhan.
我們要找的女孩絕對是雷漢

41
00:07:54,030 --> 00:07:56,670
I'll tell you when I come back but I have to stay here another day.
我回來的時候會告訴你，但我不得不在這裏再呆一天

42
00:07:57,430 --> 00:07:58,830
Nevra...
內芙拉……

43
00:07:58,950 --> 00:08:00,590
chief Tolga is suspended.
托爾加局長被停職了

44
00:08:02,990 --> 00:08:04,630
Are you serious? Why?
你是認真的嗎？為什麼？

45
00:08:05,070 --> 00:08:06,150
We don't know.
我們不知道

46
00:08:06,590 --> 00:08:09,870
Nobody knows. Firuz will take his place temporarily.
冇有人知道  菲魯茲會暫時取代他的位置

47
00:08:11,830 --> 00:08:15,990
The chief is packing up today. I think you should be here to say your farewells.
院長今天收拾行囊，我想你應該在這裏和他告別

48
00:08:16,110 --> 00:08:17,190
O.K.
好

49
00:08:19,590 --> 00:08:22,280
He tells me to organize a fancy dress party where all the guests are...
他讓我組織一次盛裝聚會，聚會上所有客人都要……

50
00:08:22,310 --> 00:08:23,950
dressed in " Dog Killer" costumes.
穿著“狗殺手”服裝

51
00:08:24,270 --> 00:08:27,670
He says "bring the gun too. I'll be there to finish somebody off".
他說：“還要帶上槍，我會在那裏殺人的。”

52
00:08:29,510 --> 00:08:32,030
What shall I do? Set up a party?
我該怎麼辦？舉辦聚會？

53
00:08:34,110 --> 00:08:39,550
You're right. But let's say we don't cooperate. The guy killed 11 people.
你是對的，但是假如說我們不合作  兇手已經殺死了11個人

54
00:08:40,430 --> 00:08:41,750
Do you think he'd leave me alone?
你以為他會放過我嗎？

55
00:08:49,070 --> 00:08:50,910
- Hi guys. - Hi mum.
-大家好-媽媽

56
00:08:53,990 --> 00:08:55,310
Deva...
德瓦

57
00:08:56,270 --> 00:08:58,670
can I talk to you in private?
我可以私下跟你說話嗎？

58
00:09:02,830 --> 00:09:03,830
O.K
好

59
00:09:05,430 --> 00:09:06,750
See you later Süveyda.
待會見蘇薇達

60
00:09:14,230 --> 00:09:15,350
What is so important?
有什麼重要的事嗎？

61
00:09:16,550 --> 00:09:17,550
Your dad called.
你爸爸打電話了

62
00:09:19,470 --> 00:09:20,470
What did he say?
他說什麼？

63
00:09:22,430 --> 00:09:23,510
He says me misses us.
他說很想念我們

64
00:09:24,750 --> 00:09:25,510
So?
然後呢？

65
00:09:25,710 --> 00:09:28,110
So...
然後……

66
00:09:28,350 --> 00:09:29,630
he wants us back.
他要我們回去

67
00:09:29,870 --> 00:09:31,830
He says he'll book and pay for our flight.
他說他要訂票並為我們的航班付款

68
00:09:32,470 --> 00:09:34,470
"Otherwise I'll come and get you myself" he says.
他說：“否則我會過來把票給你。”

69
00:09:36,510 --> 00:09:38,150
So, he is planning to kidnap us.
所以他打算綁架我們

70
00:09:38,950 --> 00:09:43,510
Not exactly. But you know your dad. He can be very impatient.
不完全是  但是你知道你的父親  他可能會很著急

71
00:09:47,030 --> 00:09:49,750
But he doesn't care about what we want.
但是他不在乎我們想要什麼

72
00:09:51,510 --> 00:09:52,790
And what did you tell him?
那你怎麼跟他說的？

73
00:09:53,110 --> 00:09:55,870
"Deva started school and I found a job. We have a new life now."
“ Deva開始上學，找到了工作，我們現在有了新的生活”

74
00:09:56,070 --> 00:09:57,710
Didn't you tell him that?
你冇告訴他嗎？

75
00:09:57,950 --> 00:09:59,110
Of course I did.
我當然告訴他了

76
00:09:59,910 --> 00:10:03,590
But he says "don't worry, school is not a big issue, we'll figure something out".
但是他說：“不用擔心，學校不是大問題，我們會解決的”

77
00:10:03,710 --> 00:10:05,230
Mum...
媽……

78
00:10:05,470 --> 00:10:07,550
that's exactly why my dad wanted to get divorced.
這就是為什麼我的父親要離婚

79
00:10:08,630 --> 00:10:10,950
He had enough of you going along with everything he said.
他受夠了你對他百依百順

80
00:10:11,150 --> 00:10:12,990
As if he was your only connection with life.
好像他是你生命中唯一的聯係

81
00:10:13,550 --> 00:10:15,710
He was suffocating because you made him feel like...
他幾乎要窒息了，因為你讓他感到……

82
00:10:15,830 --> 00:10:17,150
the world revolved around him.
世界圍繞著他旋轉

83
00:10:18,150 --> 00:10:20,110
And now he is upset because we are not there.
現在他很沮喪，因為我們不在那

84
00:10:21,190 --> 00:10:24,230
That's normal, because he's got no one to boss around.
那是正常的，因為那個男人冇有別人能指使了

85
00:10:24,790 --> 00:10:27,750
The person you call "that man" is your father. He looked after me.
你叫“那個男人”的人是你父親  他很照顧我

86
00:10:30,630 --> 00:10:31,710
Your mum is ill, son.
兒子  媽媽病了

87
00:10:31,950 --> 00:10:32,710
I know.
我知道

88
00:10:32,950 --> 00:10:35,870
Your mum is an alcoholic.
你媽媽是酒鬼

89
00:10:37,390 --> 00:10:40,590
I'll still be an alcoholic even if I quit drinking.
即使戒酒，我還是個酒鬼

90
00:10:41,670 --> 00:10:43,110
That's how it will always be.
就是這樣

91
00:10:43,830 --> 00:10:48,430
And your father put up with me. He looked after me. Understand?
你父親能夠容忍我  他照顧我  明白嗎？

92
00:10:49,750 --> 00:10:52,150
Your illness has got nothing to do with being alcoholic.
你的病與酗酒無關

93
00:10:53,150 --> 00:10:54,550
Your problem is something else.
你的問題是別的

94
00:10:55,310 --> 00:11:00,670
You become the slave of whoever looks after you. That's your illness.
你成為了照顧你的人的奴隸  這才是病根

95
00:11:01,110 --> 00:11:03,590
You are addicted to people, not alcohol.
你沈迷於人，而不是酗酒

96
00:11:23,030 --> 00:11:24,350
Girls!
女孩們！

97
00:11:24,990 --> 00:11:26,550
What are you doing?
你在做什麼？

98
00:12:04,630 --> 00:12:07,470
You've said it was impossible. How did it happen?
你已經說不可能了，這是怎麼發生的？

99
00:12:07,710 --> 00:12:09,550
I have been looking at the wrong floor.
我一直在錯誤的看著地闆

100
00:12:09,670 --> 00:12:11,430
I should've been looking further up.
我應該一直往上看

101
00:12:11,950 --> 00:12:14,590
- How much further up? - Very much.
-還有多高？-非常非常高

102
00:12:16,310 --> 00:12:19,390
That's why I am telling you the pack it in. Because it's too dangerous.
這就是為什麼我告訴你打包的原因，因為太危險了

103
00:12:20,150 --> 00:12:22,430
Do you remember when we were at the university?
你還記得我們上大學的時候嗎？

104
00:12:22,670 --> 00:12:24,870
Remember the dreams we had?
還記得我們的夢想嗎？

105
00:12:25,070 --> 00:12:28,230
Sure I do. We were planning to change the world.
當然，我們曾計畫改變世界

106
00:12:29,670 --> 00:12:32,710
But what happened? We changed our world.
但是發生了什麼事  我們改變了我們的世界

107
00:12:36,110 --> 00:12:42,190
I can't breathe here. Not enough oxygen. I want to go back to school days.
我不能在這裏呼吸  氧氣不足  我想回到學校

108
00:12:43,630 --> 00:12:44,630
It's up to you.
由你決定

109
00:13:17,590 --> 00:13:18,910
What are you going to do now?
你現在要怎麼做？

110
00:13:18,990 --> 00:13:22,270
I'll arrest him. What else? Just tell me, is it really him?
我會逮捕他  還有什麼？隻要告訴我，真的是他嗎？

111
00:13:22,950 --> 00:13:26,310
99 percent. But you won't go in alone, will you?
99％的可能性  但你不會一個人進去，對嗎？

112
00:13:27,070 --> 00:13:28,590
At least let chief Tolga know.
至少讓托爾加局長知道

113
00:13:29,830 --> 00:13:32,230
From now on, I am the one to be reported to.
從現在開始，你嚮我匯報

114
00:13:33,310 --> 00:13:35,590
Tolga is suspended. I am replacing him.
托爾加被停職了  我要接替他

115
00:13:37,230 --> 00:13:40,070
- Are you serious? - It was inevitable.
-你是認真的嗎？-這是不可避免的

116
00:13:40,830 --> 00:13:43,270
Look at me, I am working like a donkey.
看看我，我像驢一樣勤奮工作

117
00:13:44,550 --> 00:13:46,750
All Tolga was doing laying on his back.
托爾加什麼都冇幹

118
00:13:47,830 --> 00:13:49,990
You are a dodgy man. You've got it in for Nevra.
你這個狡猾的人  你已經對內芙拉下手了

119
00:13:50,110 --> 00:13:53,510
Didn't you say you'll catch the man before she does?
你不是說你會在她之前先抓住兇手嗎？

120
00:13:54,270 --> 00:13:56,110
- See this? - What?
-看到這個嗎？-什麼？

121
00:13:56,350 --> 00:13:58,750
The mark left by Nevra's slap.
內夫拉的耳光留下的印記

122
00:13:58,870 --> 00:14:01,030
I see it every morning when I look at the mirror.
我每天早晨看鏡子時都會看到

123
00:14:10,110 --> 00:14:11,190
It is Zuhal.
是祖哈爾

124
00:14:11,630 --> 00:14:12,830
Strange.
奇怪

125
00:14:19,070 --> 00:14:21,110
Hello? Hi Zuhal.
餵？ 你好 祖哈爾

126
00:14:23,950 --> 00:14:25,510
Yes, he is here.
是的，他在這裏

127
00:14:27,350 --> 00:14:28,670
Hang on.
別掛斷

128
00:14:29,470 --> 00:14:30,470
O.K darling.
好的，寶貝

129
00:14:32,950 --> 00:14:35,790
Zuhal, how are you sweetheart?
祖哈爾，你好嗎？

130
00:14:37,550 --> 00:14:38,950
Pardon?
什麼？

131
00:14:39,910 --> 00:14:41,670
What do you mean?
你什麼意思？

132
00:14:43,430 --> 00:14:44,950
So sudden?
這麼突然嗎

133
00:14:46,390 --> 00:14:47,910
Dear oh dear!
親愛的，親愛的！

134
00:14:48,230 --> 00:14:50,070
Why?
為什麼？

135
00:14:52,030 --> 00:14:53,470
O.K, I see.
好的我明白了

136
00:14:54,110 --> 00:14:55,870
We'll talk later.
我們以後再說

137
00:14:58,470 --> 00:15:00,150
O.K, I've got to go.
好啦  我掛了

138
00:15:03,070 --> 00:15:04,710
My silly daughter.
我的傻女兒

139
00:15:05,470 --> 00:15:07,870
What is it? Something bad happened?
什麼事？發生什麼事了？

140
00:15:08,630 --> 00:15:09,950
They are going back.
他們要回去了

141
00:15:10,710 --> 00:15:13,670
- Where? - Australia.
-去哪裏？-澳洲

142
00:15:14,750 --> 00:15:16,190
Immediately.
馬上就走

143
00:15:16,630 --> 00:15:19,670
Such a shame. You only just got back together.
真可惜  你們才團聚不久

144
00:15:22,390 --> 00:15:24,910
She said "urgent". Did something bad happened?
她說“緊急”有什麼不好的事嗎？

145
00:15:26,230 --> 00:15:29,070
- She made up with her husband. - That's nice.
-她和丈夫和好了-很好

146
00:15:29,710 --> 00:15:30,910
That's good news.
那是好消息

147
00:15:31,230 --> 00:15:32,790
It is so sudden.
太突然了

148
00:15:35,390 --> 00:15:37,590
I've just gotten used to them.
我剛習慣他們

149
00:15:39,230 --> 00:15:42,830
Is it alright if we leave tonight? I want to see them.
如果我們今晚離開可以嗎？我想見他們

150
00:15:44,550 --> 00:15:47,830
That's fine. I'll go and pack my suitcase.
冇關係  我去收拾行李

151
00:15:50,150 --> 00:15:51,150
Agah...
阿加

152
00:15:51,750 --> 00:15:52,870
don't be upset.
不要難過

153
00:15:53,630 --> 00:15:56,910
It was nice to have somebody around, a voice in the house.
有人在家裏感覺很好

154
00:15:58,230 --> 00:16:01,710
Now, I'll go back to being alone.
現在，我要回到孤獨中去

155
00:16:17,990 --> 00:16:19,510
I am ready. We can go.
我準備好了，我們可以走了

156
00:16:25,190 --> 00:16:30,110
-We can leave right away. -No rush. Let's eat first.
-我們可以馬上離開  -不要著急  讓我們先吃飯

157
00:16:32,510 --> 00:16:33,910
Then we can leave.
吃完再走

158
00:16:35,870 --> 00:16:37,830
Boss...
老大

159
00:16:38,390 --> 00:16:40,310
you can take it to the administrative court...
你可以抗訴行政法院

160
00:16:40,350 --> 00:16:41,910
even all the way to council of state.
甚至一直到州議會

161
00:16:42,230 --> 00:16:43,750
There'll be no use.
冇用了

162
00:16:46,910 --> 00:16:48,110
What are you going to do?
你會怎樣做？

163
00:16:48,750 --> 00:16:53,110
First, I have to remove the sand bag. But it's not going to be easy.
首先，我要把沙袋搬走，但並不容易

164
00:16:53,990 --> 00:16:56,070
Then I'll go and see may children.
然後我要去看看孩子

165
00:16:57,150 --> 00:16:59,550
I'll say to them "daddy is back, I'll be home from now on".
我要對他們說：“爸爸回來了，從現在開始我就回家了”

166
00:16:59,790 --> 00:17:03,950
"The never-ending shift has finally ended. Your dad is here now".
