336
00:30:23,630 --> 00:30:26,150
you did me good. I won't let you go.
你對我很好  我不會讓你走

337
00:30:27,670 --> 00:30:30,310
Cemil, think sensibly.
塞米爾，好好思考一下

338
00:30:32,270 --> 00:30:36,310
O.K, we have a thing going. But Deva has a future there.
好吧，我們之間有了火花，但是德瓦有一個未來

339
00:30:38,270 --> 00:30:39,670
I have a house there.
我在那裏有房子

340
00:30:41,110 --> 00:30:42,630
I'll bring that house down Zuhal.
我把那房子搬過來  祖哈爾

341
00:30:49,390 --> 00:30:50,390
What?
什麼事？

342
00:30:54,990 --> 00:30:56,070
O.K, that's good.
好  那很好

343
00:30:57,470 --> 00:30:58,670
Where are you now?
你現在在哪裏？

344
00:30:59,030 --> 00:31:00,430
I'll be there right away.
我馬上去

345
00:31:01,070 --> 00:31:05,670
First, we have to sort out our own issues.
首先，必須解決我們的問題

346
00:31:07,110 --> 00:31:08,710
Then I'll deliver the goods.
然後我再去送貨

347
00:31:11,070 --> 00:31:13,070
- What do you want? - We'll talk about it.
-你想要什麼？-我們會談的

348
00:31:13,590 --> 00:31:15,110
Who is this man? What's his problem?
這個人是誰？他有什麼問題？

349
00:31:15,350 --> 00:31:17,110
I don't know. But we'll find out.
我不知道  但我們會找到答案的

350
00:31:19,190 --> 00:31:21,790
I'll let you know if we come to a deal.
如果我們達成協議，我會讓你知道的

351
00:31:27,470 --> 00:31:28,470
B... stard!
畜生！

352
00:31:30,430 --> 00:31:31,950
What is it, something bad?
什麼事？壞事嗎？

353
00:31:32,150 --> 00:31:34,910
Yes, it is. He does exactly the same.
是的，他也是一樣

354
00:31:35,550 --> 00:31:37,070
Who is he? What's going on?
他是誰？怎麼了？

355
00:31:37,310 --> 00:31:40,790
You're all the same. First, you make me believe things.
你們都是一樣的  首先，你讓我相信一切

356
00:31:41,990 --> 00:31:43,750
Then you betray me.
然後就背叛我

357
00:31:44,830 --> 00:31:46,470
What did I do to you?
我對你做了什麼？

358
00:31:46,590 --> 00:31:47,990
Nothing but favours.
隻有恩惠

359
00:31:49,430 --> 00:31:50,710
Shame on you.
你太無恥了

360
00:31:51,150 --> 00:31:53,230
You are nothing like your father.
你一點都不像你父親

361
00:32:02,510 --> 00:32:04,510
I hope whoever is behind this slander rots in hell.
我希望在這個在背地裏誹謗的人在地獄裏腐爛

362
00:32:06,270 --> 00:32:07,710
I know nothing about pimping.
我對拉皮條一無所知

363
00:32:08,470 --> 00:32:09,550
What are you talking about?
你在說什麼？

364
00:32:11,630 --> 00:32:15,990
Now Mr Sungur, if you're going to be all tensed up...
現在，桑古爾先生，如果你要全神貫註

365
00:32:16,110 --> 00:32:18,630
we can take you down the station where you can relax a bit.
我們可以帶你到警察局放鬆一下

366
00:32:19,710 --> 00:32:22,230
Look, officers...
你看  長官……

367
00:32:22,750 --> 00:32:24,950
I have nothing to do with pimping or anything.
我和拉皮條無關

368
00:32:27,030 --> 00:32:29,590
Tell me, how did you manage to disguise yourself all these years?
告訴我，這些年來你如何掩飾自己？

369
00:32:31,070 --> 00:32:32,390
You have no criminal record.
你冇有犯罪記錄

370
00:32:35,750 --> 00:32:37,950
I wonder if you happen to know a judge or something.
我想知道你是否碰巧認識法官

371
00:32:38,070 --> 00:32:40,790
