例如，穆罕默德·尤爾吉爾

372
00:32:41,670 --> 00:32:43,950
- Do you know him? - No, I don't.
-你認識他嗎？-不，我不知道

373
00:32:44,510 --> 00:32:45,790
I don't know any judge.
我不認識任何法官

374
00:32:49,630 --> 00:32:50,710
Nevra...
內芙拉

375
00:32:51,150 --> 00:32:53,110
can you excuse us for a minute?
你能回避一下嗎？

376
00:33:06,870 --> 00:33:11,670
Look, I swear I know nothing. I don't know Reyhan or any other girl.
聽著，我發誓我一無所知  我不認識雷漢或其他女孩

377
00:33:12,350 --> 00:33:14,630
You can ask anybody.
你可以問任何人

378
00:33:16,830 --> 00:33:19,110
I am not involved in anything like that.
我冇有參與過這樣的事情

379
00:33:19,750 --> 00:33:22,390
We did ask. They said you are a pimp.
我們確實問過  他們說你就是皮條客

380
00:33:24,790 --> 00:33:26,110
F... cking b..stards.
該死的畜生！

381
00:33:27,310 --> 00:33:30,030
Yes, you're right. Unfortunately you can never trust people.
是的，你是對的  不幸的是你永遠不能信任別人

382
00:33:31,230 --> 00:33:35,070
I myself was a victim of a slander once. That's how I know.
我自己曾經是誹謗的受害者  那就是我的經驗

383
00:33:39,790 --> 00:33:44,270
Once, we detained a man who later claimed that we tortured him.
一次，我們拘留了一個人，他後來聲稱我們對他施加了酷刑

384
00:33:46,150 --> 00:33:47,230
I said no way.
我說不可能

385
00:33:47,870 --> 00:33:50,510
Son of a b... tch even got a report from a hospital...
那個畜生甚至從醫院得到報告

386
00:33:50,710 --> 00:33:53,030
claiming that we broke his bones.
聲稱我們打斷了他的骨頭

387
00:33:55,310 --> 00:33:56,710
I said he probably did it himself.
我說他可能自己做的

388
00:33:59,550 --> 00:34:01,630
Banging his arms and legs to a wall.
將他的胳膊和腿撞到牆上

389
00:34:03,510 --> 00:34:05,350
He was planning to take us to court.
他打算把我們告上法庭

390
00:34:06,430 --> 00:34:11,150
Luckily internal affairs ruled out investigation and the case closed.
幸運的是，內政排除了調查工作，案件結案

391
00:34:15,390 --> 00:34:16,710
Appropriate outcome.
合理的結果

392
00:34:17,150 --> 00:34:19,230
Yeah, otherwise. We would've been in deep shit.
是的，否則我們會陷入睏境

393
00:34:23,270 --> 00:34:26,670
That's why I understand you. Being falsely accused is a bad thing.
這就是為什麼我了解你被錯誤指控是多麼糟糕

394
00:34:27,310 --> 00:34:29,150
Because I had not broken any bones.
因為我冇有打斷任何一根骨頭

395
00:34:30,030 --> 00:34:32,430
I had stuck a truncheon up his a..s instead.
我把警棍塞到他菊花裏了

396
00:34:34,190 --> 00:34:37,550
I think he was too ashamed to tell the doctors.
我覺得他可能很羞愧，無法告訴醫生

397
00:34:38,550 --> 00:34:40,830
I wouldn't be so upset if he told the truth.
如果他說了實話，我就不會那麼心煩意亂了

398
00:34:42,990 --> 00:34:44,510
But he was lying.
但是他說謊

399
00:34:44,950 --> 00:34:46,590
He was saying I broke his arm.
他說我打斷了胳膊

400
00:34:51,510 --> 00:34:53,590
So, your wife has passed away.
那麼你老婆過身了

401
00:34:53,710 --> 00:34:56,310
Yes, she's gone. May she rest in peace.
是的，她走了  願她安息

402
00:34:56,630 --> 00:34:58,510
What do you do about cooking?
你如何做飯？

403
00:34:59,830 --> 00:35:02,190
There is a girl. She comes around and does it for me.
有一個女孩  她過來為我做

404
00:35:03,070 --> 00:35:05,910
Do you like pastry, like, pies and things?
你喜歡糕點，餡餅和東西嗎？

405
00:35:06,350 --> 00:35:08,310
- Yeah, I do. - Good.
-是的，我喜歡  -很好

406
00:35:11,150 --> 00:35:13,150
So, you must have a rolling pin.
那麼，你一定有一個搟麵杖

407
00:35:27,230 --> 00:35:31,470
O.K Mr Agah, spill the beans. What's your problem with Kambura?
好的，阿格先生，該交待了。你和坎佈拉有什麼瓜葛？

408
00:35:33,670 --> 00:35:35,070
It was 1995.
1995年

409
00:35:37,710 --> 00:35:40,430
I was transferred to Kambura Court House.
我被調到坎佈拉法院

410
00:35:43,510 --> 00:35:45,790
In the beginning everything was good.
一開始一切都很好

411
00:35:46,870 --> 00:35:49,190
People were pleasant and hospitable.
人們愉快而熱情好客

412
00:35:50,470 --> 00:35:51,910
And Kambura was a nice place.
坎佈拉是個很不錯的地方

413
00:35:53,870 --> 00:35:57,550
I said to my late wife that we came to a nice place...
我對我已故的妻子說我們來了一個好地方

414
00:35:57,670 --> 00:36:00,510
that we are out of the hustle-bustle of Istanbul.
我們脫離了伊斯坦佈爾的喧囂

415
00:36:05,430 --> 00:36:06,950
In 1996...
1996年

416
00:36:11,430 --> 00:36:13,710
a 14 year old girl committed suicide.
一名14歲女孩自殺

417
00:36:14,950 --> 00:36:17,230
She used to live with her granny.
她生前和奶奶住在一起

418
00:36:17,430 --> 00:36:19,190
Poor girl was an orphan.
可憐的女孩是一個孤兒

419
00:36:20,630 --> 00:36:21,910
Her name was Reyhan.
她的名字叫雷漢

420
00:36:24,750 --> 00:36:26,070
I received the file.
我收到文件

421
00:36:27,470 --> 00:36:29,430
The police report said "heavy depression".
警方報告稱“重度抑鬱癥”

422
00:36:29,550 --> 00:36:31,310
And the case was closed.
而且已經結案了

423
00:36:32,950 --> 00:36:36,550
One day, her granny turned up, holding a notebook.
一天，她的奶奶來了，拿著一個筆記本

424
00:36:39,510 --> 00:36:43,830
She said it belonged to her grandchild but couldn't read it as she was illiterate.
她說這是她的孫女的，但由於她是文盲看不懂

425
00:36:44,710 --> 00:36:47,270
She said her grandchild wouldn't take her life in her own accord.
她說她的孫子不會無緣無故自殺

426
00:36:47,870 --> 00:36:51,070
She said something must've happened to her.
她說她一定發生了什麼事

427
00:36:52,590 --> 00:36:55,070
She said it may be in this notebook. I want you to take a look.
她說可能在這個筆記本上  我要你看看

428
00:36:56,070 --> 00:36:57,510
And so I did.
所以我看了

429
00:36:58,270 --> 00:37:00,110
It was her diary.
那是她的日記

430
00:37:03,390 --> 00:37:05,470
She'd written down everything.
她寫下了一切

431
00:37:06,870 --> 00:37:09,510
Every single name in Kambura was in the diary.
日記中坎佈拉的每個名字

432
00:37:11,710 --> 00:37:13,110
Even from outside.
甚至還有外人

433
00:37:15,390 --> 00:37:17,030
For example, a judge.
例如法官

434
00:37:18,550 --> 00:37:20,990
He used to visit Kambura every now and then.
他曾經不時拜訪坎佈拉

435
00:37:22,630 --> 00:37:24,030
So, he knew too.
所以他也知道

436
00:37:26,230 --> 00:37:28,830
Judges, teachers...
法官，老師……

437
00:37:29,790 --> 00:37:31,790
crooks, cops...
騙子，警察……

438
00:37:33,310 --> 00:37:35,270
poor and the rich...
窮人和富人……

439
00:37:36,270 --> 00:37:38,110
the educated, the ignorant...
有文化的  冇文化的……

440
00:37:43,790 --> 00:37:46,190
She was only 12 years old at the time.
她當時隻有12歲

441
00:37:48,790 --> 00:37:50,110
Only 12.
隻有12歲

442
00:37:50,350 --> 00:37:52,390
- Reyhan stop. - Stay away.
-雷漢停下-別過來

443
00:37:52,870 --> 00:37:53,870
Reyhan!
雷漢！

444
00:37:55,590 --> 00:37:56,790
- Don't. - Away!
-不要-走開！

445
00:37:58,110 --> 00:37:59,510
Reyhan, stop.
雷漢停下

446
00:38:03,110 --> 00:38:04,110
Away!
走開！

447
00:38:07,830 --> 00:38:08,830
Let me go.
放開我

448
00:38:09,550 --> 00:38:10,750
Let me go.
放開我

449
00:38:27,030 --> 00:38:28,230
For 2 years...
整整兩年……

450
00:38:30,190 --> 00:38:34,030
all these men raped the poor girl.
這些人都強奸過那個可憐的女孩

451
00:38:38,070 --> 00:38:40,270
53 of them in total.
共53個人

452
00:38:42,870 --> 00:38:46,350
The poor girl couldn't take it anymore and she took her own life.
這個可憐的女孩受不了了，她選擇自殺

453
00:38:50,870 --> 00:38:52,390
She'd become anybody's item.
她會成為任何人的泄欲工具

454
00:38:55,550 --> 00:38:59,390
I don't know who but apparently a boy gives her a false hope of marriage.
我不知道是誰，但顯然是一個男孩錯誤的給了她婚姻希望

455
00:39:01,150 --> 00:39:03,110
He makes a move on her.
他對她採取了行動

456
00:39:03,310 --> 00:39:07,030
She doesn't decline, thinking that they were going to get married anyway.
她不拒絕，以為他們無論如何都會結婚

457
00:39:08,950 --> 00:39:12,870
Then he begins to threaten her, forcing her to be with others too.
然後他開始威脅她，迫使她也和別人在一起

458
00:39:13,950 --> 00:39:16,110
She gets frightened.
她很害怕

459
00:39:18,910 --> 00:39:20,790
She thinks it will be just a one-time thing.
她認為這隻是免洗的事情

460
00:39:20,990 --> 00:39:22,910
But the men keep coming, one after the other.
但是男人們源源不斷，一個接一個

461
00:39:22,950 --> 00:39:24,230
Like flies around honey.
像蜂蜜一樣

462
00:39:25,790 --> 00:39:27,190
Then they brought her to me.
然後他們把她帶給我

463
00:39:28,310 --> 00:39:30,150
I thought I could make some cash.
我以為我可以賺點錢

464
00:39:31,910 --> 00:39:34,190
We have a barn just over there.
我們那邊有一個穀倉

465
00:39:35,710 --> 00:39:40,430
She worked for couple of months. Then she killed herself.
她工作了幾個月，然後自殺了

466
00:39:47,630 --> 00:39:48,910
You s..n of a b... tc!
你這個狗娘養的畜生！

467
00:39:49,270 --> 00:39:51,110
I am going to ruin your f... cking life.
我要毀了你的生活

468
00:39:51,670 --> 00:39:53,190
S..n of a b... tch!
畜生！

469
00:39:54,590 --> 00:39:56,470
What did you do after reading the diary?
看完日記後你做了什麼？

470
00:39:56,790 --> 00:40:00,510
What can I do? I had an 11-year-old daughter.
我該怎麼辦？我有一個11歲的女兒

471
00:40:03,230 --> 00:40:07,710
I thought I should move her away. So, I sent her to a boarding school.
我認為應該把她送走  所以我送她去了寄宿學校

472
00:40:08,710 --> 00:40:12,190
She had to get out of Kambura. Because these men were everywhere.
她必須離開坎佈拉，因為這些男人無處不在

473
00:40:12,630 --> 00:40:14,150
What did you do about Reyhan?
你對雷漢做了什麼？

474
00:40:16,350 --> 00:40:18,950
Didn't you hand the diary over to D.A? No trial was set?
你不是將日記交給了檢察長了嗎？冇有安排庭審嗎？

475
00:40:19,830 --> 00:40:24,190
I was going to hand it to the D.A. But his name was in the diary too.
我本來要交給檢察長的，但是他的名字也在日記裏

476
00:40:25,830 --> 00:40:28,150
My hand was tied. I was scared.
我無能為力，我很害怕

477
00:40:29,230 --> 00:40:33,150
There were so many of them. And I was just a simple civil servant.
他們人太多了，我隻是一個小小的公務員

478
00:40:35,670 --> 00:40:37,750
I thought they can walk all over me.
我以為他們把我踏平

479
00:40:38,630 --> 00:40:42,430
The girl was gone anyway. What's the use of taking the case to the court?
無論如何，那個女孩已經死了，將案件提交法院又能怎樣？

480
00:40:43,110 --> 00:40:45,150
It was not going to bring her back.
不會把她帶回來

481
00:40:48,550 --> 00:40:50,190
F..cking sh... t!
該死！

482
00:40:50,830 --> 00:40:53,230
After a while, I got transferred to Istanbul.
過了一段時間，我轉到了伊斯坦佈爾

483
00:40:54,870 --> 00:40:56,630
But I never forgot about Reyhan.
但我從未忘記雷漢

484
00:40:57,950 --> 00:41:00,670
I left Kambura. But I was never able to leave Reyhan.
我離開了坎佈拉，但我再也無法放下雷漢

485
00:41:04,510 --> 00:41:07,230
10 years ago, I bought a gun.
10年前，我買了槍

486
00:41:09,070 --> 00:41:10,710
I wanted to kill someone.
我想殺人

487
00:41:12,790 --> 00:41:14,430
I tried but failed.
我嘗試過但是失敗了

488
00:41:17,590 --> 00:41:19,310
I tried again...
我再次嘗試……

489
00:41:21,070 --> 00:41:22,270
but failed again.
但又失敗了

490
00:41:24,670 --> 00:41:27,630
What made you start killing them all?
是什麼讓你開始殺死所有人？

491
00:41:32,550 --> 00:41:34,710
I was diagnosed with Alzheimer's Disease.
我被診斷出患有阿爾茨海默氏病

492
00:41:37,230 --> 00:41:40,190
I thought to myself "you are running out of time".
我對自己說：“你冇時間了”

493
00:41:41,470 --> 00:41:44,430
It will come a day you'll forget about Reyhan.
總有一天，你會忘掉雷漢

494
00:41:45,750 --> 00:41:49,590
You'll forget about Reyhan who has been in your mind for 22 years.
你會忘記這個在你的腦海中已有22年的雷漢

495
00:41:52,630 --> 00:41:55,590
Was Cemil Havran in the diary too? Is that why you went to him?
塞米爾·哈夫蘭也在日記中嗎？這就是你去找他的原因？

496
00:41:56,110 --> 00:41:58,110
Whole of Kambura took care of him.
整個坎佈拉都照顧過他

497
00:41:58,310 --> 00:42:00,510
Business owners, civil servants.
企業主，公務員

498
