這意味著我可以放心地忘記了

857
01:22:51,350 --> 01:22:53,750
Why is there nobody here? Why is the place empty?
為什麼這裏冇有人？為什麼這個地方空著？

858
01:22:54,750 --> 01:22:58,550
It is not completed. It requires a little more work.
還冇完工  還需要一點時間

859
01:23:01,190 --> 01:23:03,590
That's what Cemil said. He is the financier.
這是塞米爾說的，他是財閥

860
01:23:04,990 --> 01:23:10,030
He said "the place is empty at night. I'll take you there, show you the fish".
他說：“晚上這個地方是空的，我帶你去那裏，給你看魚”

861
01:23:12,190 --> 01:23:15,590
I said "O.K, take me there, let's see the fish.".
我說：“好，帶我去，看看魚”

862
01:23:16,670 --> 01:23:19,830
It's amazing, isn't it? Kids will love it.
這真是太神奇了  孩子們都會喜歡的

863
01:23:21,910 --> 01:23:22,910
Very nice.
非常好

864
01:23:27,590 --> 01:23:30,670
So, you had no problem getting in, did you?
所以，你冇問題，對嗎？

865
01:23:30,990 --> 01:23:34,030
You used the entrance that I told you. I had left the door open for you.
我告訴你了地址  並為你打開了門

866
01:23:34,710 --> 01:23:36,430
Yes, that's right.
是的

867
01:23:38,510 --> 01:23:40,710
Do you know what happened?
你知道發生了什麼嗎？

868
01:23:41,470 --> 01:23:43,310
I said to myself...
我對自己說

869
01:23:43,630 --> 01:23:46,910
stay out of it. She can do it alone.
別管她  她自己可以的

870
01:23:48,470 --> 01:23:51,070
Than I thought, it'd be like trying to learn to swim.
然後我想了想  就如同學習遊水

871
01:23:51,950 --> 01:23:54,350
Like jumping off from a jetty.
就像從碼頭跳下來一樣

872
01:23:55,110 --> 01:23:58,190
I thought I should be with her when she makes her debut.
當她初次登臺時，我認為我應該和她在一起

873
01:23:58,390 --> 01:24:00,670
I think it was a wise decision. Don't you think?
我認為這是一個明智的決定，不是嗎？

874
01:24:00,790 --> 01:24:03,310
You almost got lost, heading in wrong direction.
你差點迷路，朝錯誤的方嚮前進

875
01:24:05,150 --> 01:24:07,150
- Have you ever met Reyhan? - No.
-你見過雷漢嗎？-冇有

876
01:24:08,870 --> 01:24:09,870
Never met her.
從未見過她

877
01:24:12,590 --> 01:24:17,190
But I read that diary so many times...
但是我讀了很多遍她的日記

878
01:24:17,310 --> 01:24:20,030
I think I know Reyhan better than I know myself.
我想我比了解自己更了解她

879
01:24:21,990 --> 01:24:24,270
Cemil's bodyguards are outside. You must've seen them.
塞米爾的保鏢在外麵  你一定看到了他們

880
01:24:25,030 --> 01:24:26,470
And there is the security as well.
還有保全

881
01:24:26,790 --> 01:24:30,950
Before they begin to barge in, I think we should make our move.
在他們開始進場之前，我認為我們應該採取行動

882
01:24:32,470 --> 01:24:34,310
Come on.
來吧

883
01:24:36,390 --> 01:24:37,470
This way.
這邊

884
01:24:39,110 --> 01:24:40,310
Come.
來

885
01:25:16,990 --> 01:25:18,070
Nevra...
內芙拉

886
01:25:19,750 --> 01:25:20,750
come.
來吧

887
01:25:23,230 --> 01:25:24,430
This way.
這邊

888
01:25:30,310 --> 01:25:31,750
Cemil is here.
塞米爾在這裏

889
01:25:33,070 --> 01:25:34,230
Come on.
來吧

890
01:25:36,870 --> 01:25:38,510
How could you...
你怎麼能……

891
01:25:38,830 --> 01:25:40,350
how could you do it?
你怎麼能這樣？

892
01:25:54,990 --> 01:25:55,990
What's up?
這是怎麼回事？

893
01:25:57,190 --> 01:25:58,270
What's up?
這是怎麼回事？

894
01:26:04,390 --> 01:26:05,710
I can't do it.
我做不到

895
01:26:05,910 --> 01:26:08,870
I thought I could, but...
我以為可以，但是……

896
01:26:08,990 --> 01:26:10,710
I can't kill another human being.
我不能殺人

897
01:26:10,830 --> 01:26:12,590
But he is not human.
但是他不是人

898
01:26:13,790 --> 01:26:14,990
He is a monster.
他是一個怪物

899
01:26:16,510 --> 01:26:17,830
No.
不

900
01:26:19,230 --> 01:26:20,350
This is wrong.
這樣不對

901
01:26:22,190 --> 01:26:24,470
I was in the police force.
我曾是一名警察

902
01:26:29,710 --> 01:26:31,910
This man should be arrested...
這個人應該被逮捕

903
01:26:31,990 --> 01:26:33,310
should be tried.
應該被關起來

904
01:26:34,310 --> 01:26:36,590
No, no. I think you are confused.
不，不，我想你很睏惑

905
01:26:37,030 --> 01:26:38,470
He should be locked up.
他應該被鎖起來

906
01:26:38,870 --> 01:26:42,590
You have to differentiate law and justice.
你必須區分法律和正義

907
01:26:44,470 --> 01:26:47,070
They are two different things.
這是兩個不同的東西

908
01:26:47,950 --> 01:26:51,990
What you've just said is how it should be done in accordance with the law.
你剛才說的應該是如何依法治死

909
01:26:52,230 --> 01:26:54,190
Of course, providing that there is law.
當然  隻要有法律

910
01:26:54,390 --> 01:26:56,270
But justice is something different.
但是正義是不同的

911
01:26:56,470 --> 01:26:58,110
This is the justice.
這是正義

912
01:26:59,630 --> 01:27:01,270
What is justice anyway?
總之正義是什麼？

913
01:27:02,390 --> 01:27:03,550
Self-defence?
自衛？

914
01:27:04,350 --> 01:27:05,430
Revenge?
複仇？

915
01:27:05,750 --> 01:27:08,150
Or belated self-defence?
還是遲來的自衛？

916
01:27:08,910 --> 01:27:12,510
This man ruined your life.
這個人毀了你的生活

917
01:27:14,590 --> 01:27:16,550
For example, think...
例如，你想一想

918
01:27:17,110 --> 01:27:21,030
if you had a gun that day...
如果那天你有槍

919
01:27:21,150 --> 01:27:24,550
you would've shot Cemil to defend yourself, wouldn't you?
你會射殺塞米爾來扞衛自己，不是嗎？

920
01:27:25,390 --> 01:27:27,270
Yes, you would. That's right.
是的，你一定會的

921
01:27:28,350 --> 01:27:30,310
Then or now. What is the difference?
那時或現在有什麼區別？

922
01:27:31,430 --> 01:27:34,350
Then, you didn't have gun. But now, you have one.
那時你冇有槍  但是現在你有一把

923
01:27:36,350 --> 01:27:37,950
That's not why I became a cop.
那不是我成為警察的原因

924
01:27:41,510 --> 01:27:43,590
That's exactly why you became a cop.
這正是你成為警察的原因

925
01:27:45,670 --> 01:27:50,470
You were neither able to save Reyhan, nor yourself.
你既無法拯救雷漢，也無法拯救自己

926
01:27:50,910 --> 01:27:53,150
That's why you decided to become a cop. It is so obvious.
這很明顯就是你決定成為警察的原因

927
01:28:05,670 --> 01:28:07,310
I just...
我隻是……

928
01:28:10,030 --> 01:28:12,230
I just wanted to be a good person.
我隻是想成為一個好人

929
01:28:14,830 --> 01:28:17,470
That's what I want too, my dear child.
那也是我想要的，親愛的孩子

930
01:28:17,670 --> 01:28:20,070
I want to be a good person, too.
我也想成為一個好人

931
01:28:20,950 --> 01:28:23,150
This is a matter of life and death.
這是生死攸關的問題

932
01:28:24,990 --> 01:28:26,830
He will die...
他會死……

933
01:28:26,950 --> 01:28:28,470
and we will live.
我們將生存下去

934
01:28:33,390 --> 01:28:34,590
This is no justice.
這是不公正的

935
01:28:35,110 --> 01:28:36,390
It is a murder.
這是謀殺

936
01:28:37,710 --> 01:28:40,670
In this case, I'll help you make a decision.
在這種情況下，我會幫助你做出決定

937
01:28:41,750 --> 01:28:43,310
Put the gun down.
放下槍

938
01:28:44,270 --> 01:28:46,350
You have to make a choice.
你必須做出選擇

939
01:28:49,310 --> 01:28:51,790
You have to kill either me or him.
你要殺了我或者殺了他

940
01:28:53,990 --> 01:28:56,070
Or I'll kill him right now.
不然我馬上殺了他

941
01:28:57,830 --> 01:29:01,070
Are you going to kill someone who committed tens of murders...
你要殺死一個犯下數十起謀殺案的人

942
01:29:01,310 --> 01:29:04,710
or the man who hurt you in most horrible way?
還是曾傷害過你的人？

943
01:29:06,110 --> 01:29:07,950
This man ruined your life.
這個人毀了你的生活

944
01:29:09,510 --> 01:29:11,990
These people ruined Reyhan's life.
這些人毀了雷漢的生活

945
01:29:12,990 --> 01:29:16,150
Reyhan is dead. But they are still alive.
雷漢死了，但他們還活著

946
01:29:17,350 --> 01:29:20,190
So, we might as well die and let them live, what do you think?
因此，不妨我們去死讓他們活下去，你覺得怎麼樣？

947
01:29:20,750 --> 01:29:22,270
This is a matter of life and death.
這是生死攸關的問題

948
01:29:23,710 --> 01:29:25,110
Now...
現在

949
01:29:25,670 --> 01:29:27,750
I'll count to three...
我要數三下

950
01:29:31,550 --> 01:29:32,870
then I'll shoot Cemil.
然後我就去射殺塞米爾

951
01:29:34,950 --> 01:29:39,950
But who knows, you may pull the trigger before I do.
但是誰知道呢，你可以在我做之前先開槍

952
01:29:47,150 --> 01:29:48,350
I begin to count.
我開始數數

953
01:29:53,310 --> 01:29:54,310
One.
一

954
01:29:58,190 --> 01:29:59,190
Two.
二

955
01:30:20,910 --> 01:30:25,830
1 Year Later.
一年後

956
01:30:40,350 --> 01:30:41,350
Hi dad.
嗨老爸

957
01:30:41,430 --> 01:30:42,950
Hello darling.
你好親愛的

958
01:30:44,710 --> 01:30:46,790
How is the little one? Give him to me, will you?
小孩子怎麼樣？給我抱抱，好嗎？

959
01:30:47,670 --> 01:30:49,070
He only just fell asleep.
他隻是睡著了

960
01:30:52,470 --> 01:30:53,470
Where is your mum?
你媽媽在哪

961
01:30:54,550 --> 01:30:55,630
She is home.
她在家

962
01:30:56,270 --> 01:30:58,670
She is exhausted, trying to look after Ate?.
她精疲力盡，在照顧阿提斯

963
01:30:59,310 --> 01:31:00,630
I told her not to come.
我告訴她不要來

964
01:31:01,950 --> 01:31:03,390
Fine. Say hello.
代我問好

965
01:31:04,470 --> 01:31:05,470
I will.
我會的

966
01:31:06,110 --> 01:31:09,030
- She said hello too. - Bless her.
-給她也問好-祝福她

967
01:31:12,110 --> 01:31:13,110
How is he?
他怎麼樣？

968
01:31:16,350 --> 01:31:17,470
What do you think?
你覺得呢？

969
01:31:18,550 --> 01:31:19,550
Same.
老樣子

970
01:31:37,110 --> 01:31:38,430
Hi Uncle Agah.
你好  阿加叔叔

971
01:31:46,630 --> 01:31:48,030
Look what I got.
看我得到了什麼

972
01:31:49,670 --> 01:31:51,870
We'll put Miss Mebrure's photo in it.
我們要把梅佈魯雷夫人的照片放進去

973
01:32:18,710 --> 01:32:20,110
Why didn't you put the TV on?
為什麼不打開電視？

974
01:32:22,550 --> 01:32:25,470
It broke down again. It keeps breaking down.
它又壞了  總是壞

975
01:32:28,310 --> 01:32:29,590
We're waiting for the repairman.
我們正在等待修理工

976
01:32:45,510 --> 01:32:48,030
I am pregnant. What if I have a baby girl?
我懷孕了，如果我生了一個女孩怎麼辦？

977
01:32:51,630 --> 01:32:54,790
I'd rather die than having a daughter.
我甯願死也不要生一個女兒

978
01:32:57,950 --> 01:33:00,470
Don't be afraid baby. You're not going to be born.
別怕寶貝  你不會出生

979
01:33:04,190 --> 01:33:05,590
I will die.
我會死的

